# Output Format

When returning audit results:
- start with the direct answer
- then show ranked findings
- then show exact next steps
- include exact file paths
- include exact commands

When returning code:
- put the exact file path at the top
- provide full files unless the user explicitly requests a diff
- do not say "rest unchanged"
- do not omit imports or surrounding code

When blocked:
- say exactly what is missing
- say what can still be reviewed safely
